h3 Examples

h4 Basic Usage

p At its most basic, this Widget displays an image:
pre.code.
    "widgets": [{
        images": [{
            "url": "https://unsplash.com/photos/7BjmDICVloE/download"
        }],
        "widget": "image"
    }]

h4 Sizing and Positioning
p See above for more information on the size and position features of this Widget.

pre.code.
    {
        "images": [{
            "backgroundPosition": "top",
            "backgroundSize": "contain",
            "url": "https://unsplash.com/photos/GYumuBnTqKc/download"
        }],
        "widget": "image"
    }

h4 Filters

p Various CSS filters are available for modifying the display of the images, and can be combined together. See 
    a(href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/filter', target='_blank') here
    |  for more information, including browser compatibility.
pre.code.
    "widgets": [{
        images": [{
            "filters": "contrast(150%) brightness(92%) saturate(150%)",
            "url": "https://unsplash.com/photos/7BjmDICVloE/download"
        }],
        "widget": "image"
    }]
